ong the Normans. In the later Middle Ages it was overtaken by   John  , but continued to run second to that name until the 20th century, when the picture became more fragmented."],"variants":[]},{"name":"II","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["1  ♂ ‘Wondrous’ or ‘enlightenment’.","2  ♀ ‘Fine jade’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"William II Chester was born in 1400, in Stafford, Staffordshire, England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 daughter with Mrs William Chester II. He died in 1480, in his hometown, at the age of 80."},"et":{"1400–1480":"1400–1480","1405–Female":"1405–Surnud","1425–1512":"1425–1512","1425":"1425","1512":"1512","1400":"1400","1480":"1480","1405":"1405","Stafford, Staffordshire, England":"Stafford, Staffordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Stafford, Staffordshire, England, United Kingdom":"Stafford, Staffordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1400–1480":"1400–1480","1405–Female":"1405–Kuollut","1425–1512":"1425–1512","1425":"1425","1512":"1512","1400":"1400","1480":"1480","1405":"1405","Stafford, Staffordshire, England":"Stafford, Staffordshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Stafford, Staffordshire, England, United Kingdom":"Stafford, Staffordshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1400–1480":"1400–1480","1405–Female":"1405–Décédée","1425–1512":"1425–1512","1425":"1425","1512":"1512","1400":"1400","1480":"1480","1405":"1405","Stafford, Staffordshire, England":"Stafford, Staffordshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Stafford, Staffordshire, England, United Kingdom":"Stafford, Staffordshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"William II Chester est né en 1400, à Stafford, Staffordshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fille avec Mrs William Chester II. Il est décédé en 1480, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 80 ans."},"de":{"1400–1480":"1400–1480","1405–Female":"1405–Verstorben","1425–1512":"1425–1512","1425":"1425","1512":"1